==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Monitor nozzle
<hw>Monitor nozzle</hw>. <def>A nozzle capable of turning completely
round in a horizontal plane and having a limited play in a vertical
plane, used in hydraulic mining, fire-extinguishing apparatus,
etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Monitorship</ent>⟦br⟧
